00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,360
what I want,

594
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:49,000
or why I want a divorce.

595
00:37:51,599 --> 00:37:52,360
Forget it.

596
00:37:54,519 --> 00:37:55,119
Forget it.

597
00:37:55,119 --> 00:37:55,639
Again,

598
00:37:55,639 --> 00:37:56,719
you stop halfway.

599
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,760
If you don't know, you can ask me.

600
00:37:59,280 --> 00:37:59,800
No.

601
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:00,519
Why do you have to

602
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:01,360
keep guessing?

603
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,760
We are all adults.

604
00:38:03,079 --> 00:38:04,519
We are tired from work every day.

605
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:06,280
If you want something,

606
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,159
just tell me directly.

607
00:38:07,159 --> 00:38:07,760
I'll do it.

608
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,960
Isn't that better?

609
00:38:14,119 --> 00:38:15,360
If in life,

610
00:38:16,039 --> 00:38:17,719
everything has to be asked for,

611
00:38:20,599 --> 00:38:22,079
I'd rather not have such a marriage.

612
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:39,920
Hello?

613
00:38:42,119 --> 00:38:43,519
Why did it take so long to answer?

614
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,679
What are you doing?

615
00:38:46,119 --> 00:38:46,960
Of course,

616
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,880
I'm eating.

617
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:52,199
What did you eat?

618
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:55,239
Spicy chicken, stir-fried pork,

619
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:57,400
and braised pork ribs.

620
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,679
Pass.

621
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,119
How about you?

622
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,360
You skipped class.

623
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:05,400
How's your painting?

624
00:39:08,239 --> 00:39:09,119
Let me correct that.

625
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:10,360
I didn't skip class.

626
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:12,159
I asked my aunt for permission.

627
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:13,519
I'm on leave.

628
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,199
You were the one

629
00:39:16,199 --> 00:39:17,519
who skipped the most classes in school.

630
00:39:17,519 --> 00:39:19,199
Now you're a decent person.

631
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,000
Have you eaten yet?

632
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,119
I'm in the restaurant right now.

633
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,719
Restaurant?

634
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:29,920
The restaurant is so quiet.

635
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,320
I'm in the private room.

636
00:39:34,599 --> 00:39:36,599
Do you think I can't even tell

637
00:39:36,599 --> 00:39:38,000
the echo of the studio?

638
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:39,760
Wan

639
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,280
I brought you some fried rice.

640
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,280
I saw you were busy,

641
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,400
so I didn't bring it over.

642
00:39:44,519 --> 00:39:45,320
Remember to eat it.

643
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,559
I'm leaving. Remember to eat it.

644
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:47,760
Thank you, Xin'er.

645
00:39:48,039 --> 00:39:50,559
So you ate spicy chicken,

646
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:53,320
stir-fried pork, and braised pork ribs.

647
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:54,599
And your colleague

648
00:39:54,599 --> 00:39:55,880
brought you fried rice.

649
00:39:56,119 --> 00:39:56,760
Right?

650
00:40:00,159 --> 00:40:01,199
Alright, alright.

651
00:40:01,199 --> 00:40:02,119
You should find a restaurant

652
00:40:02,119 --> 00:40:02,920
and have a proper meal.

653
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,119
Don't lecture me.

654
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:05,639
Zhou Wan,

655
00:40:06,039 --> 00:40:06,960
put down

656
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:07,679
everything you're working on

657
00:40:07,679 --> 00:40:08,519
and go eat.

658
00:40:08,519 --> 00:40:09,320
Xiao Liu.

659
00:40:09,719 --> 00:40:11,119
Alright.

660
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,639
You should also find a restaurant

661
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:14,840
and have a proper meal.

662
00:40:15,719 --> 00:40:16,519
Okay?

663
00:40:19,519 --> 00:40:21,159
Alright, I'll listen to you.

664
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,159
I'll hang up now.

665
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:27,440
Bye-bye.

666
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:39,159
Xiaoliu, come here.

667
00:40:39,679 --> 00:40:40,320
Xiaoliu.

668
00:40:40,679 --> 00:40:41,280
Come here.

669
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,519
Who let you eat my sandwich?

670
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:50,480
Back then, the project wasn't standardized.

671
00:40:51,079 --> 00:40:52,320
and there were no digital archives.

672
00:40:52,519 --> 00:40:53,360
It's hard to find.

673
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:57,000
It's okay. I just want to see

674
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,119
if there's anything

675
00:40:58,119 --> 00:40:59,159
we can learn from the second phase.

676
00:41:00,079 --> 00:41:00,760
I found it.

677
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,199
Don't worry.

678
00:41:08,199 --> 00:41:09,719
I've spoken to Mr. Lu.

679
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:10,639
If there are any issues,

680
00:41:10,639 --> 00:41:11,760
just have him come to me.

681
00:41:12,079 --> 00:41:12,559
Okay.

682
00:41:12,559 --> 00:41:14,199
Please sign here.

683
00:41:14,679 --> 00:41:15,199
Okay.

684
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:20,800
Okay.

685
00:41:21,559 --> 00:41:23,159
Shall I deliver it to your office?

686
00:41:23,199 --> 00:41:23,679
No need.

687
00:41:23,679 --> 00:41:24,719
I'll handle it myself.

688
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:26,000
You should be off work now.

689
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:27,800
Alright, I'll be on my way then.

690
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:10,639
The acquisition price for Jun'an Building Materials Factory

691
00:42:10,639 --> 00:42:11,559
is so low.

692
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:27,480
The degree of soil pollution

693
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:29,199
exceeds the initial assessment.

694
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:39,159
Zhou Wan,

695
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:41,239
so the one you want to deal with

696
00:42:41,239 --> 00:42:42,159
is Lu Zhongyue.

697
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:44,639
Is this the reason

698
00:42:45,079 --> 00:42:46,159
